HEADWORD: Capcase
<hw>Cap"case`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A small traveling
case or bandbox; formerly, a chest.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>A <qex>capcase</qex> for your linen and your plate.</q>
